ygData.messageBody:
I am a human in Qeynos and I just hit level 8 tonight. Before I go off and
waste money on spells that don't work, I was hoping to get some feedback
from people on the list as to the best spells at level 8 to purchase and
why. Also perhaps if anyone could clue me in as to where in my area is a
good place to kill and how to apply the old and new spells to gaining xp and
loot I would greatly appreciate it. Thank you ahead of time!

P.S.
Don't die twice right when you make a level. I had made 8 and lost it just
as quickly as I got it. Didn't even have time to enjoy it before I was
struggling to get back to it :)

Dalthor
Level 8 Necromancer
TestServer
